              <table id="EditorialReviewsPanel" class="ReviewSection" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"><tr><td>
	
                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Mark McCormack provides information that may be new even to experienced negotiators. He describes the qualities of a good negotiator; the features of a win/win negotiation; the most effective (and most desperate) negotiating tactics; and how to reconcile different negotiating styles when they collide.</span>
              
</td></tr></table>
